s=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">w</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cardinality</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">\\</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">w</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">}))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"k\">else</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
